title: Ep. 355 - Our Collective Plunge Into Madness
description:
Today we'll continue to talk about the two big stories the media is ignoring. First, the 7-year-old boy whose mother was just granted full custody and the ability to "transition" him into a girl against his father's wishes. Second, the sex scandal involving a prominent Democratic female congresswoman. The media might not be interested in these stories, but that doesn't mean they aren't important. Date: 10-23-2019
